::if false::
<!--
    Force redirect to the right hostname.
    It is needed to redirect `path` to `path/` with the correct domain name.
    See the "Caveats" section of http://strd6.com/2016/02/github-pages-custom-domain-with-ssltls/.
-->
::end::
::if api.isDefined("hostname")::
<script type="text/javascript">
if (location.hostname != "::api.getValue("hostname")::") {
	window.location.replace("https://::api.getValue("hostname")::" + location.pathname);
}
</script>
::end::